<div class="dablink">This article is about the mineral.  For the gemstone, see <a href="/wiki/Diamond_(gemstone)" title="Diamond (gemstone)">Diamond (gemstone)</a>.  For other uses, including the shape <big><a href="/wiki/%E2%97%8A" title="◊">◊</a></big>, see <a href="/wiki/Diamond_(disambiguation)" title="Diamond (disambiguation)">Diamond (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
